normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4a0/42cf/171_normal.png?m=1630576706", "title": "投资", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/invest", "topics": 2129, "footer": "", "header": "Can you make money with money?", "title_alternative": "Invest", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a4a0/42cf/171_mini.png?m=1630576706", "stars": 3243, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 171, "parent_node_name": "money"}, "member": {"id": 37679, "username": "coetzee", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/coetzee", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "青岛", "tagline": "Getting things done", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6a30/7655/37679_mini.png?m=1676449249", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6a30/7655/37679_normal.png?m=1676449249", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6a30/7655/37679_large.png?m=1676449249", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6a30/7655/37679_xlarge.png?m=1676449249", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6a30/7655/37679_xlarge.png?m=1676449249", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6a30/7655/37679_xlarge.png?m=1676449249", "created": 1366182571, "last_modified": 1676449249}, "last_reply_by": "zbowen66", "last_touched": 1735312947, "title": "2024 年即将结束，大家来说一下自己的 2024 年股市赚了还是赔了，收益率是多少，分享下 2025 年的理财计划", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1100585", "created": 1735260898, "deleted": 0, "content": "我先来，股市+黄金基金总，收益 36%左右，现在股市基本空仓，持有少部分标普", "content_rendered": "我先来，股市+黄金基金总，收益 36%左右，现在股市基本空仓，持有少部分标普", "last_modified": 1735260982, "replies": 110, "id": 1100585}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e223/0b85/509_large.png?m=1515388901", "name": "pet", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e223/0b85/509_normal.png?m=1515388901", "title": "宠物", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/pet", "topics": 486, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "宠物", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e223/0b85/509_mini.png?m=1515388901", "stars": 333, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 509, "parent_node_name": "naturalist"}, "member": {"id": 72899, "username": "xubingok", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/xubingok", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8e46/807f/72899_mini.png?m=1684458443", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8e46/807f/72899_normal.png?m=1684458443", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8e46/807f/72899_large.png?m=1684458443", "created": 1409804831, "last_modified": 1684458443}, "last_reply_by": "Comyn", "last_touched": 1735314755, "title": "猫晚上喜欢刨门和叫唤.影响睡觉.有啥好办法吗?", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1100605", "created": 1735264028, "deleted": 0, "content": "![]( https://res.cloudinary.com/xubingok/image/upload/v1735263675/blog/7d215491e7ceedb8610ed416db0465c2.jpg)\r\n\r\n领养的一只猫.在我家有一年了.晚上喜欢刨卧室的门(后来发现其实是刨门口的地板).或者在客厅叫唤.\r\n\r\n买了网上所谓的驱猫神器,挂在门把手上,没啥用.\r\n\r\n夏天的时候,到了晚上睡觉时就把猫关阳台了...反正猫砂盆和吃的喝的都在阳台.\r\n\r\n现在冬天了,关在阳台怕冻死...就晚上留在客厅.\r\n\r\n结果昨晚迷迷糊糊应该是 4,5 点的样子被吵醒了,各种刨门,各种叫唤...很无奈.\r\n\r\n是公猫,两岁了,已绝育.\r\n\r\n放进卧室是不行的,猫喜欢跑床上去...\r\n毕竟宠物天天地上跑,和宠物一个被窝睡觉我做不到.\r\n\r\n有啥好办法吗?", "content_rendered": "<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/xubingok/image/upload/v1735263675/blog/7d215491e7ceedb8610ed416db0465c2.jpg\"/></p>\n<p>领养的一只猫.在我家有一年了.晚上喜欢刨卧室的门(后来发现其实是刨门口的地板).或者在客厅叫唤.</p>\n<p>买了网上所谓的驱猫神器,挂在门把手上,没啥用.</p>\n<p>夏天的时候,到了晚上睡觉时就把猫关阳台了...反正猫砂盆和吃的喝的都在阳台.</p>\n<p>现在冬天了,关在阳台怕冻死...就晚上留在客厅.</p>\n<p>结果昨晚迷迷糊糊应该是 4,5 点的样子被吵醒了,各种刨门,各种叫唤...很无奈.</p>\n<p>是公猫,两岁了,已绝育.</p>\n<p>放进卧室是不行的,猫喜欢跑床上去...\n毕竟宠物天天地上跑,和宠物一个被窝睡觉我做不到.</p>\n<p>有啥好办法吗?</p>\n", "last_modified": 1735264028, "replies": 104, "id": 1100605}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_large.png?m=1651385965", "name": "android", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_normal.png?m=165138596